column7: The story of Nell Smith & The Flaming Lips is as improbable and unexpected as their album full of Nick Cave covers. Existing in a triangular universe of mutual admiration, _Where the Viaduct Looms_ gave us the opening track tonight, the menacing “Red Right Hand”.
Originally from Nick Cave + the Bad Seeds
